      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;masked-multihead-self-attention&#34;&gt;Masked Multihead Self-attention&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;img width=&#34;793&#34; alt=&#34;스크린샷 2023-03-29 10 39 24&#34; src=&#34;https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/75467530/230662201-337365b6-f416-43ba-9216-28d1ddd5fd15.png&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;cross-attention&#34;&gt;Cross attention&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Encoder-decoder attention&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/75467530/230662934-714e2ebc-ce15-4d72-a70b-7de616f5a9ca.png&#34; alt=&#34;transformer_resideual_layer_norm_3&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;reference&#34;&gt;Reference&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://tigris-data-science.tistory.com/entry/%EC%B0%A8%EA%B7%BC%EC%B0%A8%EA%B7%BC-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-Transformer4-Masked-Multi-Head-Attention%EA%B3%BC-Decoder&#34;&gt;https://tigris-data-science.tistory.com/entry/%EC%B0%A8%EA%B7%BC%EC%B0%A8%EA%B7%BC-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-Transformer4-Masked-Multi-Head-Attention%EA%B3%BC-Decoder&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
